♪You said you would be with me♪

13
00:01:32,260 --> 00:01:35,180
=Six Sisters=

14
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:38,140
=Episode 38=

15
00:01:38,990 --> 00:01:41,400
I still hope you can save Jiaxi.

16
00:01:42,430 --> 00:01:43,840
Say no more. I understand.

17
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:45,280
You sit down first.

18
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:46,630
Sit.

19
00:01:50,550 --> 00:01:52,320
So, what do we do?

20
00:01:53,550 --> 00:01:55,160
Shall we go to Hefei?

21
00:01:55,160 --> 00:01:56,510
- Ok.
- No problem.

22
00:01:56,790 --> 00:01:57,840
I'll book hotel rooms.

23
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:59,150
Don't, Jiahuan.

24
00:01:59,150 --> 00:02:00,120
I'll do that.

25
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,840
Don't book one for me.

26
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:05,200
I'm pregnant. I can't do the donation.

27
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:07,320
You guys go try your luck.

28
00:02:10,630 --> 00:02:11,510
Hongyu,

29
00:02:12,150 --> 00:02:12,990
I'll also go.

30
00:02:14,230 --> 00:02:15,470
Jiaxi made mistakes.

31
00:02:16,950 --> 00:02:18,080
But she can't die.

32
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:20,000
Mom,

33
00:02:20,390 --> 00:02:21,990
you don't have to go.

34
00:02:22,510 --> 00:02:23,350
Xiaoling,

35
00:02:24,440 --> 00:02:25,840
no pressure.

36
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:27,680
Stay at home with Mom.

37
00:02:28,040 --> 00:02:29,350
We'll go there

38
00:02:29,350 --> 00:02:30,430
and try our luck.

39
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:31,640
Fine.

40
00:02:38,620 --> 00:02:40,760
♪Sisters♪

41
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:43,370
♪Remain thin♪

42
00:02:43,780 --> 00:02:48,480
♪Like the crescent moon♪

43
00:02:49,090 --> 00:02:51,330
♪Sisters♪

44
00:02:51,670 --> 00:02:53,850
♪Work hard♪

45
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:59,610
♪Like the flowing river♪

46
00:03:00,320 --> 00:03:04,230
♪We went through hardships♪

47
00:03:04,670 --> 00:03:09,480
♪When the world kept changing♪

48
00:03:10,620 --> 00:03:15,120
♪We traveled everywhere♪

49
00:03:15,900 --> 00:03:22,380
♪We braved the storm together♪

50
00:03:23,380 --> 00:03:25,670
♪We drink and care for each other♪

51
00:03:25,830 --> 00:03:26,710
I hope

52
00:03:27,670 --> 00:03:29,640
at least one of us will be a match.

53
00:03:30,480 --> 00:03:31,320
I hope it's me.

54
00:03:32,760 --> 00:03:33,640
I'm younger.

55
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:35,840
You're just a little bit younger.

56
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:39,870
None of us are really young.

57
00:03:41,410 --> 00:03:42,840
There will be a way out.

58
00:03:42,980 --> 00:03:46,580
♪We drink and care for each other♪

59
00:03:46,790 --> 00:03:50,650
♪As time goes by,
we still care for each other♪

60
