♪Everybody gathers
when it's brightly lit♪

61
00:03:54,950 --> 00:03:58,720
♪We're always happy and lively♪

62
00:04:00,570 --> 00:04:04,130
♪We drink and care for each other♪

63
00:04:04,440 --> 00:04:07,200
♪As time goes by,
we still care for each other♪

64
00:04:07,200 --> 00:04:10,630
♪Everybody gathers
when it's brightly lit♪

65
00:04:10,630 --> 00:04:17,600
♪We're always happy and lively♪

66
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:32,910
Hongyu.

67
00:04:35,630 --> 00:04:37,230
I don't want to continue the therapy.

68
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:42,000
According to the result,

69
00:04:42,590 --> 00:04:43,760
only Jiali is a match.

70
00:04:44,950 --> 00:04:46,080
I'll go beg her.

71
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,230
She can help us.

72
00:04:51,390 --> 00:04:52,280
I beg you.

73
00:04:53,030 --> 00:04:54,560
I beg you, Hongyu.

74
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:55,840
Let me die.

75
00:04:56,760 --> 00:04:58,840
I'm too ashamed to see Jiali.

76
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:09,000
Jiaxi,

77
00:05:11,030 --> 00:05:12,560
your life isn't just your concern.

78
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:13,470
Listen carefully.

79
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:16,880
If you die, how will Xiaoman live?

80
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,150
How will Mom live?

81
00:05:20,840 --> 00:05:21,710
We promised

82
00:05:21,710 --> 00:05:23,150
to take care of Mom forever.

83
00:05:23,150 --> 00:05:24,000
However hard it is,

84
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,000
you must hang in there.

85
00:05:26,950 --> 00:05:28,640
You can't die before Mom.

86
00:05:33,390 --> 00:05:34,230
And...

87
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:38,280
How could I live without you?

88
00:05:43,440 --> 00:05:44,910
We made a lot of mistakes.

89
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:48,880
I'll go beg Jiali.

90
00:05:49,390 --> 00:05:50,280
I'll beg her

91
00:05:50,710 --> 00:05:51,840
to save your life.

92
00:05:54,590 --> 00:05:55,880
When you recover,

93
00:05:55,880 --> 00:05:57,150
we'll correct and repent.

94
00:05:57,150 --> 00:05:58,030
We'll make it up.

95
00:05:59,390 --> 00:06:01,110
That is if you can survive.

96
00:06:03,580 --> 00:06:05,230
It's so painful.

97
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:09,960
It's ok.

98
00:06:26,150 --> 00:06:27,200
Hongyu.

99
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:29,670
How did it go?

100
00:06:31,030 --> 00:06:31,910
Hongyu,

101
00:06:32,590 --> 00:06:33,550
what is the result?

102
00:06:34,270 --> 00:06:35,280
Is there a match?

103
00:06:35,660 --> 00:06:36,910
What's the situation?

104
00:06:37,840 --> 00:06:39,110
Is there no match?

105
00:06:41,900 --> 00:06:43,280
Say something.

106
00:06:50,180 --> 00:06:51,060
Jiali,

107
00:06:52,500 --> 00:06:53,660
please save Jiaxi.

108
00:06:54,540 --> 00:06:56,260
No one but you can save her now.

109
00:06:59,820 --> 00:07:01,020
So, she can be saved.

110
00:07:03,260 --> 00:07:04,100
Yeah.

111
00:07:08,340 --> 00:07:09,580
Hongyu, get up.

112
00:07:09,580 --> 00:07:10,460
Jiali,

113
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,780
Jiaxi and I are sorry.

114
00:07:13,740 --> 00:07:15,420
We'll do anything to repay you.

115
00:07:25,180 --> 00:07:26,020
I'll save her.

116
00:07:26,180 --> 00:07:27,260
Who told you I wouldn't?

117
00:07:27,900 --> 00:07:29,300
I can't leave her to die.

118
00:07:31,540 --> 00:07:32,420
Get up.

119
00:07:42,340 --> 00:07:44,140
Let's just say
I owed her in a former life

120
00:07:44,140 --> 00:07:46,420
and now I'll repay her.

121
00:07:49,540 --> 00:07:50,660
Glad she can be saved.

122
00:07:51,780 --> 00:07:53,380
She's my sister, after all.

123
00:08:30,900 --> 00:08:32,180
Mom gave this to us.

124
00:08:32,620 --> 00:08:33,620
No password.

125
00:08:34,900 --> 00:08:35,940
(Current Savings Bankbook)

126
00:08:37,780 --> 00:08:38,620
You...

127
00:08:38,900 --> 00:08:39,980
What are you doing?

128
00:08:41,540 --> 00:08:43,300
No surgery is 100% safe.

129
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:45,780
I want to arrange everything.

130
00:08:46,420 --> 00:08:49,060
- If...
- But the surgery is said to be safe.

131
00:08:49,740 --> 00:08:50,820
It is safe.

132
00:08:51,100 --> 00:08:52,740
But when I arrange everything,

133
00:08:52,740 --> 00:08:54,220
- I'll be relieved.
- But...

134
00:08:55,420 --> 00:08:56,980
These are our bankbooks.

135
00:08:57,820 --> 00:08:59,620
They're for you. Keep them.

136
00:09:00,460 --> 00:09:01,540
This one is for Xiaonian.

137
00:09:09,940 --> 00:09:12,300
You just won't stop sacrificing yourself

138
00:09:12,820 --> 00:09:14,620
until you die.

139
00:09:14,620 --> 00:09:16,220
Don't say that.

140
00:09:16,410 --> 00:09:18,020
I'm not that great.

141
00:09:20,780 --> 00:09:23,260
Before, I lived for my family.

142
00:09:23,420 --> 00:09:25,100
Later, I thought, "Why?

143
00:09:25,100 --> 00:09:26,420
I must live for myself."

144
00:09:27,490 --> 00:09:29,100
Now, I have the old idea back.

145
00:09:30,630 --> 00:09:32,380
I think living for someone else

146
00:09:32,380 --> 00:09:33,620
and for this big family

147
00:09:34,060 --> 00:09:35,460
can also make me happy.

148
00:09:41,020 --> 00:09:42,700
I remember when Dad was alive,

149
00:09:42,700 --> 00:09:44,940
he often told me
to take care of the family

150
00:09:44,940 --> 00:09:45,980
instead of breaking it.

151
00:09:46,380 --> 00:09:47,780
Now, I think

152
00:09:48,380 --> 00:09:49,580
I'm serving my purpose well.

153
00:09:52,090 --> 00:09:53,420
I'll finish my duty.

154
00:10:17,420 --> 00:10:18,300
Jiali.

155
00:10:26,060 --> 00:10:26,970
Thank you.

156
00:10:43,380 --> 00:10:44,260
Jiali.

157
00:10:54,300 --> 00:10:57,180
(Operating room, No entering)

158
00:11:10,860 --> 00:11:14,020
(Sterile Area)

159
00:11:18,380 --> 00:11:21,060
(Six months later)

160
00:11:27,940 --> 00:11:30,380
- Are we here too early?
- What's wrong?

161
00:11:31,660 --> 00:11:32,500
- Mom.
- Then...

162
00:11:32,740 --> 00:11:34,380
Shall we take a photo here?

163
00:11:34,740 --> 00:11:37,060
- Good idea.
- Ok. I'll take it for you.

164
00:11:37,060 --> 00:11:37,940
Ok.

165
00:11:38,860 --> 00:11:40,260
Where shall we stand?

166
00:11:40,260 --> 00:11:41,180
- Here.
- Come on.

167
00:11:41,300 --> 00:11:42,340
- Here?
- Yes.

168
00:11:42,340 --> 00:11:43,620
- We'll stand here.
- Good.

169
00:11:43,620 --> 00:11:44,700
- Come on.
- Ok.

170
00:11:44,700 --> 00:11:46,460
One. Be happy.

171
00:11:46,460 --> 00:11:47,300
Two.

172
00:11:48,100 --> 00:11:48,940
Three.

173
00:11:49,140 --> 00:11:50,700
Ok. Check it.

174
00:11:51,620 --> 00:11:54,020
Uncle Fan. Let's take a family photo.

175
00:11:54,580 --> 00:11:55,420
Together.

176
00:11:57,060 --> 00:11:59,420
- Ok.
- I don't look good in photos.

177
00:11:59,420 --> 00:12:00,340
Excuse me, sir.

178
00:12:00,540 --> 00:12:02,340
Could you please take a photo for us?

179
00:12:02,340 --> 00:12:03,220
Yes, yes.

180
00:12:03,820 --> 00:12:05,650
- I don't look good in photos.
- Come on.

181
00:12:06,060 --> 00:12:08,020
Our son wants it. Just do it.

182
00:12:08,020 --> 00:12:09,140
But I always close my eyes.

183
00:12:09,140 --> 00:12:10,700
- That's ok.
- Stand closer.

184
00:12:10,700 --> 00:12:11,940
- Ok.
- Closer, please.

185
00:12:12,660 --> 00:12:15,020
Ready. One, two, three.

186
00:12:19,620 --> 00:12:20,500
Come on.

187
00:12:22,860 --> 00:12:24,180
Extra food, huh?

188
00:12:24,460 --> 00:12:26,740
I took it back from Mom's.

189
00:12:26,860 --> 00:12:28,180
Here. The same old rule.

190
00:12:28,700 --> 00:12:30,020
- You have the drumstick.
- No.

191
00:12:30,020 --> 00:12:32,140
- I have the chicken feet.
- No, no. I'll have them.

192
00:12:32,140 --> 00:12:34,260
- You eat this.
- Chicken feet are good for hair.

193
00:12:34,260 --> 00:12:35,300
No need.

194
00:12:35,300 --> 00:12:37,140
Your hair is so thick.

195
00:12:37,820 --> 00:12:39,460
I had more hair when I was little.

196
00:12:39,460 --> 00:12:40,740
I couldn't grab it with one hand.

197
00:12:40,740 --> 00:12:41,820
Come on. Eat it.

198
00:12:41,820 --> 00:12:43,100
We still have nice hair.

199
00:12:43,250 --> 00:12:45,380
Ouyang Bao is nearly bald.

200
00:12:49,500 --> 00:12:51,500
I'm always worried at this time of year.

201
00:12:51,500 --> 00:12:53,380
What if the loan sharks come?

202
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:56,940
My comrade in arms told me

203
00:12:57,340 --> 00:13:00,100
those loan sharks were arrested.

204
00:13:00,460 --> 00:13:01,560
Really?

205
00:13:02,350 --> 00:13:03,940
Then Xiaonian can come back.

206
00:13:06,940 --> 00:13:08,340
Are they here again?

207
00:13:08,940 --> 00:13:11,060
No way. I'll go check it.

208
00:13:11,060 --> 00:13:11,940
I'll go.

209
00:13:12,660 --> 00:13:14,180
Count on me if we have to fight.

210
00:13:26,140 --> 00:13:26,980
Here's a package.

211
00:13:26,980 --> 00:13:28,260
He Jiali, right?

212
00:13:28,260 --> 00:13:29,700
- Yes.
- Sign here.

213
00:13:29,700 --> 00:13:30,940
What is this?

214
00:13:30,940 --> 00:13:32,140
I didn't buy anything.

215
00:13:34,280 --> 00:13:35,140
- Here.
- Ok.

216
00:13:38,860 --> 00:13:39,780
Who sent it?

217
00:13:41,860 --> 00:13:44,340
Shanghai. Son bought it for you.

218
00:13:45,860 --> 00:13:46,700
Open it and see

219
00:13:46,700 --> 00:13:47,580
what it is.

220
00:14:17,640 --> 00:14:19,300
Looks great.

221
00:14:19,530 --> 00:14:20,540
I always wanted to buy

222
00:14:20,540 --> 00:14:21,980
a pair of shoes of this color.

223
00:14:22,420 --> 00:14:23,260
Try them on.

224
00:14:24,740 --> 00:14:26,980
No need. They must fit perfectly.

225
00:14:27,660 --> 00:14:29,340
He's doing good in Shanghai.

226
00:14:30,420 --> 00:14:31,340
That's a relief, right?

227
00:14:39,860 --> 00:14:43,700
(Huainan TAXI)

228
00:14:47,060 --> 00:14:47,940
Be right there.

229
00:14:48,860 --> 00:14:49,740
Jiali.

230
00:14:52,020 --> 00:14:53,180
Jiaxi, Hongyu.

231
00:14:53,180 --> 00:14:54,260
- Jiali.
- Come in.

232
00:14:55,300 --> 00:14:56,140
Jiali.

233
00:15:01,060 --> 00:15:02,500
- Get up.
- Get up.

234
00:15:02,500 --> 00:15:03,700
- Come on.
- Jiali.

235
00:15:04,060 --> 00:15:05,100
- Get up.
- Jiali.

236
00:15:05,100 --> 00:15:06,380
I was wrong.

237
00:15:07,100 --> 00:15:08,180
I really was wrong,

238
00:15:08,180 --> 00:15:09,060
Jiali.

239
00:15:10,220 --> 00:15:11,100
Jiali.

240
00:15:13,180 --> 00:15:17,100
I may not repay you in this life.

241
00:15:17,100 --> 00:15:19,260
But in my next life, I will.

242
00:15:19,580 --> 00:15:22,260
Come on. I've let it go.

243
00:15:22,260 --> 00:15:23,620
You can let it go, too.

244
00:15:23,620 --> 00:15:24,460
Come on.

245
00:15:26,300 --> 00:15:27,980
I'm too ashamed,

246
00:15:27,980 --> 00:15:28,980
Jiali.

247
00:15:29,540 --> 00:15:31,740
Jiali, will you forgive me?

248
00:15:31,980 --> 00:15:33,940
Fine. I forgive you.

249
00:15:34,220 --> 00:15:35,500
I forgive you.

250
00:15:35,620 --> 00:15:37,180
- I really do. Get up.
- Come on.

251
00:15:37,180 --> 00:15:38,020
Get up.

252
00:15:41,180 --> 00:15:42,140
Jiali.

253
00:15:52,240 --> 00:15:53,090
It's ok.

254
00:15:54,900 --> 00:15:57,540
It's my decision to save you.

255
00:15:57,700 --> 00:16:00,180
I've figured everything out.

256
00:16:00,780 --> 00:16:02,900
Don't think you owe me anything.

257
00:16:13,020 --> 00:16:13,980
I know.

258
00:16:15,020 --> 00:16:16,460
It's easy to forgive someone else,

259
00:16:16,580 --> 00:16:17,860
but hard to forgive yourself.

260
00:16:18,860 --> 00:16:20,700
You should learn to forgive yourself.

261
00:16:23,020 --> 00:16:24,180
Anyway,

262
00:16:24,660 --> 00:16:26,380
I want you to be healthy.

263
00:16:39,460 --> 00:16:46,460
(Spring Festival, 2009)

264
00:16:46,660 --> 00:16:49,540
(Harmony)

265
00:16:50,940 --> 00:16:52,700
It's been a really long time

266
00:16:52,700 --> 00:16:54,660
since we last have a reunion dinner.

267
00:16:57,580 --> 00:16:58,940
I'll say no more.

268
00:16:59,660 --> 00:17:00,540
Let's eat.

269
00:17:06,100 --> 00:17:06,980
Mom.

270
00:17:08,300 --> 00:17:09,620
I want to say something.

271
00:17:10,580 --> 00:17:12,220
Ok. Go ahead.

272
00:17:17,970 --> 00:17:19,140
For the sake of my weakness,

273
00:17:19,440 --> 00:17:21,940
I'll drink water instead of wine.

274
00:17:25,500 --> 00:17:26,820
I couldn't

275
00:17:28,900 --> 00:17:30,620
come to this world

276
00:17:31,740 --> 00:17:32,980
without Mom.

277
00:17:38,780 --> 00:17:41,180
I couldn't be sitting here alive

278
00:17:44,340 --> 00:17:45,620
without Jiali.

279
00:17:50,100 --> 00:17:51,980
When I nearly died,

280
00:17:52,860 --> 00:17:54,540
I did grow mature.

281
00:17:56,340 --> 00:17:57,620
I had a lot of feelings.

282
00:18:01,500 --> 00:18:03,340
I made many mistakes before.

283
00:18:04,740 --> 00:18:06,180
I'll make it up to you guys.

284
00:18:12,180 --> 00:18:15,580
Being your sister
is the greatest blessing

285
00:18:16,180 --> 00:18:17,620
I've ever had.

286
00:18:20,500 --> 00:18:22,420
